                <h3> Create an Account </h3>
            </div>
            <div style="clear:both"></div>  *@

                <div style="float:left;">
                    <img src="~/images/signin_newaccount_icon_retina.png" height="40px" />
                </div>
                <div style="float:left; padding-top:10px; padding-left:10px; ">
                    <h3> Create an Account </h3>
                </div>
                <div style="clear:both"></div> 
                 <p>Although registration is not compulsory to use our service, 
                        we recommend you to do so. By registering to our website, 
                        you can keep track of the orders you have made and many 
                        other benefits that we announce time-to-time. 
                 </p>
                    <div class="editor-label" style="max-width:90px;"></div>
                    <div class="vmenu" style="padding:8px; height:38px; width:110px;">
                        <a href="~/customer/register" style="text-decoration:none; ">Register</a>
                    </div>

            <div style="clear:both"></div>

            <br />  
        </div>      
    </div>

</div>
